<h1 class="title"> <a href="<?php echo($NEWS_PATH);?>2010-04-04_RPI_Swing_Club_Attends_The_2010_Boston_Tea_Party;_Places_Finalists_in_Competition"> RPI Swing Club Attends The 2010 Boston Tea Party; Places Finalists in Competition</a></h1>						
						
